Module com.DominionDMS.SnakeGame
Package com.DominionDMS.SnakeGame.Utils

Class Constants

java.lang.Object
com.DominionDMS.SnakeGame.Utils.Constants
public class Constants extends Object
The Constants class provides a central place to manage game-wide constant values. It includes constants for game dimensions, initial positions, speeds, and other configurations used throughout the Snake Game.
Author:
Dominion Aromolaran
